Yves De Sistelle Incidence Eau de Parfum - 100 ml (For Women) Price: Rs.1045

Incidence Perfume by Yves De Sistelle Incidence is a gorgeous fruity fragrance with a floral heart and a warm embracing base. Feminine and well balanced it has top notes of bergamot luscious pear and mandarin orange. The heart notes are iris jasmine and rose. The bottom notes are musk cedar wood and amber.
